Purpose of @JoinColumn annotation:
The @JoinColumn annotation helps us specify the column we'll use for joining an entity association or element collection.
Purpose of @ManyToOne annotation:
The ManyToOne annotation may be used within an embeddable class to specify a relationship from the embeddable class to an entity class.
